<template>
    <v-list dark>
        <template v-for="item in items">
            <template v-if="item.items && item.items.length">
                <v-list-group v-model="item.active">
                    <NavigationItem :item="item" dropdown slot="activator"/>
                    <NavigationList :items="item.items"/>
                </v-list-group>
            </template>
            <template v-else>
                <NavigationItem :item="item"/>
            </template>
        </template>
    </v-list>
</template>

<script>
    import NavigationItem from './NavigationItem';

    export default {
        name      : 'NavigationList',
        components: {NavigationItem},
        props     : {
            items: {
                type: Array
            }
        }
    }
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
</style>
